narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Good class if you want to improve your writing, fair amount of work though.

I would summarize English 114 27 as a very useful class for writing skills, that also covers a very interesting topic. It was a great balance of learning writing skills and getting to read about a very interesting topic. I would recommend English 114 because it is so useful to work on writing skills.

This is an interesting section if you're interested in the material and how consumerism affects society. Prof. Winders is actually very insightful and also very nice and understanding. I feel like my writing greatly improved and she helped me break out of my high school ways of writing. I would definitely recommend this section to anyone considering English 114. Also
